      <title>厨房日记 烘焙篇</title>
      <link href="/2020/04/25/%E5%8E%A8%E6%88%BF%E6%97%A5%E8%AE%B0-%E7%83%98%E7%84%99%E7%AF%87/"/>
      <url>/2020/04/25/%E5%8E%A8%E6%88%BF%E6%97%A5%E8%AE%B0-%E7%83%98%E7%84%99%E7%AF%87/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aplayer@latest/dist/APlayer.min.css"><script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aplayer@latest/dist/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/meting@1/dist/Meting.min.js"></script><div align="center"><font size="70">关于我第四次制作戚风蛋糕这档事</font></div><p>此篇博客仅为记录，配方学习自<strong>下厨房</strong>，作者:<a href="http://www.xiachufang.com/cook/139699972/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">小漾兒_</a></p><h3 id="戚风蛋糕"><a href="#戚风蛋糕" class="headerlink" title="戚风蛋糕"></a>戚风蛋糕</h3><p>&emsp;戚风蛋糕，烘焙界无情的杀手，小白们的噩梦。人畜无害的外表，但是B事却非常地多。<img src="https://cos-1301807709.cos.ap-chengdu.myqcloud.com/%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/%E7%83%98%E7%84%99/%E8%9B%8B%E7%B3%95.jpg" alt="蛋糕" loading="lazy"><em>就是这个货</em></p><p>&emsp;今天是我我第四次作戚风蛋糕了，前三次均已失败告终，不过这一次我将以必胜的姿态拿下胜利，<strong>哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈嘎嘎嘎</strong><br><img src="https://cos-1301807709.cos.ap-chengdu.myqcloud.com/%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/%E7%83%98%E7%84%99/20200105178874_RCiVLq.jpg" alt="冲冲冲" loading="lazy"><em>干就完了！</em></p><hr><h3 id="事前准备"><a href="#事前准备" class="headerlink" title="事前准备"></a>事前准备</h3><p><img src="https://cos-1301807709.cos.ap-chengdu.myqcloud.com/%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/%E7%83%98%E7%84%99/ok.jpg" alt="装备" loading="lazy"><em>万事俱备，只欠成功</em>  </p><p><strong>食材:</strong></p><ul><li>鸡蛋&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;三个</li><li>玉米油&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;30克</li><li>细砂糖&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;40克</li><li>牛奶&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;40克</li><li>低筋面粉&emsp;&emsp;50克</li><li>柠檬汁&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;几滴  </li></ul><p><strong>装备：</strong></p><ul><li>精确电子秤</li><li>电动打蛋机</li><li>打蛋盆（家里就一个，另一个用的碗）</li><li>蛋液分离器</li><li>蛋糕磨具（六寸）</li><li>烤箱<hr></li></ul><h3 id="开始制作"><a href="#开始制作" class="headerlink" title="开始制作"></a>开始制作</h3><p>刚刚发现<strong>下厨房</strong>居然有网页版，不过想想也是，这年头哪个正经软件还没个网站了，正好，也省的我一步一步的写了。<br><a href="http://www.xiachufang.com/recipe/104095956/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">制作教程</a></p><p>在准备好材料后，我就开始了长达一个小时半的制作过程（别问为什么这么慢，问就是仔细）  </p><p>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.  磕鸡蛋ing~<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.  </p><p>.   .<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.   &emsp;称量食材克数ing~ ~<br>.<br>.  </p><p>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.   &emsp;&emsp;打发蛋白ing~ ~ ~<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.   &emsp;&emsp;手法搅拌ing~ ~ ~ ~<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.  &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;放入烤箱  </p><p>.<br>.<br>.<br>.  &emsp;等待~<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.  &emsp;&emsp;等待~ ~ </p><p>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br> .<br>.<br>.  &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;等待~ ~ ~<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.  .<br>.<br>.<br>.  &emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;&emsp;继续等待~ ~ ~ ~ ~<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.  .<br>.<br>.<br>制作即将完成～(￣▽￣～)(～￣▽￣)～（得瑟）<br>.<br>.<br>.  <img src="https://cos-1301807709.cos.ap-chengdu.myqcloud.com/%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/%E7%83%98%E7%84%99/IMG_20200416_130032.jpg" alt="表情" loading="lazy"><em>马上就好了，好馋</em> </p><p>.<br>.<br>.  </p><p>.<br><img src="https://cos-1301807709.cos.ap-chengdu.myqcloud.com/%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/%E7%83%98%E7%84%99/665f61814ed1f1b5bc82295fc7a71832.jpg" alt="表情" loading="lazy"><strong><em>烤好了，欧耶！！！！</em></strong><br>.<br>.<br>.<br>.   </p><hr><h3 id="制作结果"><a href="#制作结果" class="headerlink" title="制作结果"></a>制作结果</h3><p><img src="https://cos-1301807709.cos.ap-chengdu.myqcloud.com/%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/%E7%83%98%E7%84%99/IMG20200425194538.jpg" alt="结果" loading="lazy"><br><strong>失败了?????！！！！！！！！！！</strong>  </p><p>………<br>………<br>………  </p><p><img src="https://cos-1301807709.cos.ap-chengdu.myqcloud.com/%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/%E7%83%98%E7%84%99/IMG_20200425_203458.jpg" alt="懵逼" loading="lazy"> </p><p><strong>为啥会塌下去啊，我的每一步都没毛病啊</strong> </p><p><img src="https://cos-1301807709.cos.ap-chengdu.myqcloud.com/006GJQvhly1g86qh1c3ycg30a00a0agk.gif" alt="哭" loading="lazy"></p><p>以后，我打死也不做戚风蛋糕了。难搞哦╥﹏╥  </p><h3 id="原因分析"><a href="#原因分析" class="headerlink" title="原因分析"></a>原因分析</h3><p>&emsp;经过查了一夜的各种配方后，原因居然是：<br>&emsp;&emsp;<strong>烤的时候打开烤箱，导致蛋糕塌陷</strong>  </p>]]></content>
      
      
